Wordpress plugin inspired by the post in css-tricks blog : <a href="http://css-tricks.com/14647-abbrs-for-web-nerd-acronymns/">css-tricks.com/14647-abbrs-for-web-nerd-acronymns/</a>

Premature version.

Actually when you enable the plugin it only filters text, and the abbrs are the ones hardcoded inside the plugin.

Future todo : 

* add personalized terms.
* decide where to apply filter, even comments or descriptions.
* decide if the plugin is enabled inside post or page.

Installation
============
Simply download file to your plugins folder, then enable it via admin.
